===========
Gewebehaken
===========

A framework to provide HTTP endpoints for incoming webhooks.

Currently supported:

- GitLab
- Twitter (via Zapier)

:Copyright: 2015-2024 `Jochen Kupperschmidt <https://homework.nwsnet.de/>`_
:License: MIT, see LICENSE for details.


